After native scrollback leaves the physical cursor on the last row, a resize must still render the next frame from the top-left of the physical terminal.
Frame area after resize: Rect { x: 0, y: 0, width: 16, height: 10 }

Physical screen after redraw:
|┌AI────────────┐|
|│              │|
|│              │|
|│              │|
|│              │|
|│              │|
|│              │|
|│              │|
|│              │|
|└──────────────┘|

The modal must not be anchored in a lower screen band.
